constants.constant:
The "Create..." submenu of FileSystem dock's context menu, or the "New" section of the main context menu when empty space is clicked. The data [Dictionary] contains:
[code]&"base_directory": String[/code] - Path to the base directory where a file should be created.
[code]&"needs_prefix": bool[/code] - Whether the option needs a "New" prefix (for consistency with native options).
[codeblock]
func _get_menu_options(data):
    if data["needs_prefix"]:
        add_context_menu_item("New Image File...", create_image)
    else:
        add_context_menu_item("Image File...", create_image)
[/codeblock]
